TCGA-BRCA data preparation

Download TCGA-BRAC data

CNV data

GDCquery link
GDCquery category pdf

library(TCGAbiolinks)
query <- GDCquery(project = "TCGA-BRCA", 
                  data.category = "Copy Number Variation",
                  data.type = "Copy Number Segment")

dir = "~/Desktop/DF/public/"

# Download files
GDCdownload(query = query, directory = dir)

# Import data 
dir = "~/Desktop/DF/public/"
# 디렉토리 내 파일 목록 확인
files <- list.files(path = paste0(dir,"TCGA-BRCA"), full.names = TRUE, recursive = TRUE)

library(plyr)
# rbind.fill을 사용하여 모든 열을 유지하면서 데이터 결합
all_data <- do.call(rbind.fill, lapply(files, function(f) {
  read.table(f, header = TRUE, sep = "\t", check.names = FALSE)
}))

all_data %>% saveRDS(paste0(dir,"TCGA_BRCA_CNV.rds"))
dir = "~/Desktop/git/template/TCGA/"
all_data = readRDS(paste0(dir,"TCGA_BRCA_CNV.rds"))

Annotate genomic regions

library(GenomicRanges)
library(AnnotationDbi)
library(org.Hs.eg.db)
library(dplyr)

# Create GRanges object
gr <- GRanges(
  seqnames = paste0("chr", all_data$Chromosome),
  ranges = IRanges(start = all_data$Start, end = all_data$End)
)

# Load TxDb
txdb <- TxDb.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg38.knownGene

# Find overlaps with known genes
overlaps <- findOverlaps(gr, genes(txdb))

# Extract information about the overlaps
overlap_info <- data.frame(
  queryHits = queryHits(overlaps),
  subjectHits = subjectHits(overlaps)
)

# Annotate the all_data with gene information
annotated_data <- all_data
annotated_data$geneId <- NA
annotated_data$geneSymbol <- NA
annotated_data$geneName <- NA

for (i in seq_len(nrow(overlap_info))) {
  hit <- overlap_info[i,]
  annotated_data[hit$queryHits, "geneId"] <- names(genes(txdb))[hit$subjectHits]
  annotated_data[hit$queryHits, "geneSymbol"] <- AnnotationDbi::select(org.Hs.eg.db, keys = names(genes(txdb))[hit$subjectHits], columns = c("SYMBOL"), keytype = "ENTREZID")[, "SYMBOL"]
  annotated_data[hit$queryHits, "geneName"] <- AnnotationDbi::select(org.Hs.eg.db, keys = names(genes(txdb))[hit$subjectHits], columns = c("GENENAME"), keytype = "ENTREZID")[, "GENENAME"]
}

# save annotated data
annotated_data %>% saveRDS(paste0(dir,"TCGA_BRCA_CNV_annotated.rds"))

Import Annotated data

dir = "~/Desktop/git/template/TCGA/"
annotated_data = readRDS(paste0(dir,"TCGA_BRCA_CNV_annotated.rds"))




TCGA-BRCA CNV Analysis

Number of patients in data

# annotated_data[1:3,]
annotated_data$GDC_Aliquot %>% unique() %>% length()
## [1] 2341

CNV information

df = annotated_data %>% filter(Copy_Number >= 0) %>% 
  dplyr::select(GDC_Aliquot) %>% table() %>% data.frame() %>% arrange(desc(Freq))
df %>% ggplot(aes(GDC_Aliquot, Freq)) + geom_col() +
  xlab("Patient ID (not shown here)") + ylab("Number of CNV information") +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_blank()) +
  labs(caption = "Patients with Copy Number Information")

CNV information by Chromosome

df = annotated_data %>% filter(Copy_Number >= 0) %>% 
  dplyr::select(GDC_Aliquot, Chromosome) %>% table() %>% data.frame() 

df %>% ggplot(aes(GDC_Aliquot, Freq, fill=Chromosome)) + 
  geom_col(color="black", size=0.1) +
  xlab("Patient ID (not shown here)") + ylab("Number of CNV information") +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_blank()) +
  labs(caption = "Patients with Copy Number Information")

CNV distribution by patient

annotated_data %>%
  filter(Copy_Number > 0) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Copy_Number, fill = GDC_Aliquot)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.size = 0.1) +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = "none", axis.text.x = element_blank()) +
  scale_x_sqrt() +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(2, 4), size = 0.2, linetype = "dashed", color = "red") +
  annotate("text", x = c(2, 4), y = -0.4, 
           label = paste0("CNV = ",c("2", "4")), vjust = 0, color = "red", size=2)

CNV distribution by patient (zoomed in)

annotated_data %>%
  filter(Copy_Number > 0) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Copy_Number, fill = GDC_Aliquot)) +
  geom_boxplot(outlier.size = 0.1) +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = "none", axis.text.x = element_blank()) +
  scale_x_sqrt() +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(2, 4), size = 0.4, linetype = "dashed", color = "red") +
  annotate("text", x = c(2, 4), y = -0.4, 
           label = paste0("CNV = ",c("2", "4")), vjust = 0, color = "red", size=3) +
  xlim(c(0, 50)) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = c(6), size = 0.4, linetype = "dashed", color = "red") +
  annotate("text", x = c(6), y = -0.4, 
           label = paste0("CNV = ",c("6")), vjust = 0, color = "red", size=3)
